 and break) as well as the GeV data.\nThe spectrum of GeV flashes is predicted to extend above 0.1 TeV, where they\ncan be detected by ground-based Cherenkov telescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2015 00:12:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
