ntal data exists. Whilst faster\ngate operations are realisable with in-plane fields for P, As, and Sb donors,\nonly for the Bi donor, our calculations predict faster gate response in the\npresence of both in-plane and out-of-plane fields, truly benefiting from the\nproposed planar field control mechanism of the hyperfine interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2015 00:23:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-29"}
