tor, which could be used to correlate\ndiscrepancies between Rate equation and Monte Carlo methods. $\\beta$ factor\nindicates the formation efficiency under various circumstances. Higher values\nof $\\beta$ indicates a lower production efficiency. We found that $\\beta$\nincreases with a decrease in rate of accretion from gas phase to grain phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2015 10:02:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-27"}
